Logout to your Vercel account

Usage: logout [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --invalidate [<BOOL>]  Invalidate the token on the server. Pass `--invalidate=false` to skip the remote revoke [default: true] [possible values: true, false]
  -h, --help                 Print help
